com.wm.xmldata

Class XmlDataTypeTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wm.xmldata.XmlDataTag
      • com.wm.xmldata.XmlDataTypeTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class XmlDataTypeTag
extends XmlDataTag
    The XmlDataTypeTag class constructs an XmlData type-tag from its constituent parts. It may also be used to parse a type-tag into its component parts. There is a methods that return the full-name which consists of just the ncName and the namespace. Type-tags are used only in the definition of XmlData Document Types and never appear in infosets. Their format is similar to attribute-tags.

    It's format is: 

     
     ncName#namespace
